Reinventing mobility

   Multimodal interchange

Challenges

   Challenges

Sustainable mobility

   Facilitating sustainable mobility: a new railway station, seamless flow
   for pedestrians and encouraging public transport as well as "soft"
   modes of transport

Quality of life

   Improving quality of life: public spaces that are both enjoyable and
   practical, new housing, shops and services developments.

Business vocation

   Strenghtening economic attractiveness: continuous growth, a more
   diverse tertiary sector, urban and architectural innovation.

